        <div class="code-item">
          <div class="code-title"><a href="https://github.com/jpbascur/orion-app" target="_blank">ORION</a></div>
          <div class="code-desc">An open-source web dashboard for exploring research institutions and funders from the CWTS OpenAlex dataset — no SQL knowledge required. Supports filtering, basket building, co-occurrence network visualization in VOSviewer, and CSV export.</div>
          <div class="code-links">
            <a class="code-link" href="https://github.com/jpbascur/orion-app" target="_blank">GitHub</a>
            <a class="code-link" href="https://orion-app-kp52msbgxa-ew.a.run.app" target="_blank">Live demo</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="code-item">
          <div class="code-title"><a href="https://github.com/jpbascur/scimacro-demo" target="_blank">SciMacro — Science Macroscope</a></div>
          <div class="code-desc">An interactive science map that clusters networks using the Leiden algorithm. Allows selecting clusters to create new maps for iterative refinement. Comes with demo data, supports uploading your own data, and allows downloading data from selected clusters.</div>
          <div class="code-links">
            <a class="code-link" href="https://github.com/jpbascur/scimacro-demo" target="_blank">GitHub</a>
            <a class="code-link" href="https://scimacro-demo-35001728336.us-central1.run.app" target="_blank">Live demo</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="code-item">
          <div class="code-title"><a href="https://github.com/jpbascur/text-similarity-maker" target="_blank">TSM — Text Similarity Maker</a></div>
          <div class="code-desc">A free web app for creating science maps from paper titles and abstracts — no citation links required. Generates text embeddings with SPECTER2, builds a cosine similarity network or a UMAP dimensionality reduction, and exports directly to VOSviewer Online.</div>
          <div class="code-links">
            <a class="code-link" href="https://github.com/jpbascur/text-similarity-maker" target="_blank">GitHub</a>
            <a class="code-link" href="https://huggingface.co/spaces/juanbascur/text-similarity-maker" target="_blank">Live demo</a>
          </div>
        </div>

